::Feline::
She jumped as HotRod walked in.  She looked down and blushed. "I had 
no..idea that..well..." SHe walked over and kissed him. "Let's just 
say that I saw the Matrix." SHe smiled and kissed him again.

SHe wondered if the chip would even be nessassary.  But then, she 
wondered how stronly he loved her.  She would leave the chip and use 
it when the time was right. 

She put her arms around him. "I want to thank you. I never knew what 
it was all about. But.." She kissed him again and purred softly while 
she kissed him, sending soft vibrations while she kissed him.  "But 
I'm glad it was you who showed me. Showed me how to trust again."
